Use the standard library
This is how to even_odd_palindrome of n:
   Remember that even is 0
   Remember that odd is 0
   Remember that i is 1
   Do this n times:
      Remember that s is tostring of i
      Remember that r is ""
      Remember that j is s's length
      Do this s's length times:
         Decrease j
         Add r to item j in s
      End do
      Remember that p is sum of s and r
      When remainder of p and 2 is 0, then:
         Increase even
      But, if not:
         Increase odd
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is [even, odd]
Now you know